title: Aleco
description: Part of the Aleco bio market chain. This well-assorted organic supermarket stocks a wide range of organic fruit and vegetable, frozen food, cereals, sweets, tea and coffee, juices, beers, wines, natural toiletry and cleaning items, local products. Has vegan spreads, tofu, soy and rice milk, vegan cheese and sausages, rice milk chocolate, soy ice cream, and even refrigerated pasta marked vegan. In-store outlet for fresh organic and wholemeal bakery items with listed ingredients and vegan breads and rolls.
